<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 Page Not Found</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
        integrity="sha384-r21iWgKRZ7vpFYdW29aKbVxIEfaRvZ+gOyGJbMieIMq8pZXTLNEyB5j1uUoMtf99"
        crossorigin="anonymous">
    <style>
        body {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .error-image {
            width: 30rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .btn {
            font-size: 1rem;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 0.25rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container text-center">
        <h1>Congratulations, you've found the 404 page!</h1>
        <p>You are seeing this page because the URL you requested does not exist. Please report to us if you think
            this is an error.</p>
        <a href="/" class="btn">Homepage</a>
        <img src="https://razorpay.com/assets/404.png" class="error-image" alt="404 Image">
    </div>
</body>

</html>
